{"tid":1308884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜無辜被波及！Twice被韓網狂攻，日籍成員宣布中止活動","createTime":"2019-07-12T04:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T13:46:43.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c1eb8bb71971cc34b6f99b91fdf3b7d115f1a452","tid":1308884,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"日韓貿易戰持續延燒，就連演藝圈也大受影響，最近韓網狂攻包含周子瑜在內的Twice， 要求團內包含Momo、Sana和Mina等三名日籍成員退團，近日Mina似乎也因為身心壓力受不 了，宣布中止活動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近日韓貿易戰雙方攻防猛烈，韓國因為日本的經濟打壓大受影響，沒想到除了經濟面， 就連演藝圈也受到波及。韓國網友首先點名擁有三名日籍成員的女子團體Twice，要求Mom o、Sana和Mina等三名日籍成員退團，讓粉絲們對於無辜的偶像非常心疼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而近日其中的日籍成員Mina似乎也因為身心承受了巨大壓力，透過經紀公司宣布患有舞台 恐慌，確定缺席接下來六場演唱會。經紀公司提到：「目前還沒有診斷出確切原因，但是 Mina對於站上舞台有著極度不安與恐懼感，討論過後決定先接受治療。」消息一出果然引 發粉絲熱議，直呼：「偶像無辜好可憐阿！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/07/11/190711-10876-2-cn0Gl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F190711-10876-2-cn0Gl.jpg&h=1d62d1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n Twice九人感情相當好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/07/11/190711-10876-3-zzmsr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F190711-10876-3-zzmsr.jpg&h=59f5ef93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因承受不了身心壓力，Mina患有舞台恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/07/11/190711-10876-5-BGlzL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F190711-10876-5-BGlzL.png&h=fe5776f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwice官網聲明全文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/07/11/190711-10876-4-wSa49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F190711-10876-4-wSa49.jpg&h=8b7ea514&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d0778a79dde48c5330158558d8f343ff69d7157","tid":1308884,"uid":138658,"like":33,"dislike":49,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"twice冇一個係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5f6a4d5b85a5ad50a8f109f4dd0bbc5d2b7c52","tid":1308884,"uid":240608,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"本土唔要 咪賣海外囉<br />\n<br />\ntwice 人氣咁高,, 場場爆"},{"pid":"ea0d5cecaadcb4a442062af74010e97a78009113","tid":1308884,"uid":171598,"like":15,"dislike":27,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"仲扮野<br />\n唔想dance就真<br />\n<br />\n佢有佢反 你有你做明星<br />\n根本唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd456970c459d08adbf9f01d469c73c2cbd94e1c","tid":1308884,"uid":171598,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9d0778a79dde48c5330158558d8f343ff69d7157","tid":1308884,"uid":138658,"like":33,"dislike":49,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"twice冇一個係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baeb8a222ec8a050abbdada8887d0c3c9330f056","tid":1308884,"uid":152432,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"ea0d5cecaadcb4a442062af74010e97a780091